  "title": "Admin Assistant (West)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Collaborate with the admin team to deliver an exceptional experience for customers across all areas of the company.</li>\n  <li>Review POs and DOs from both internal and external sources to ensure accuracy in items, quantities, and amounts.</li>\n  <li>Perform data entry and maintain accurate records.</li>\n  <li>Handle filing, document verification, and checks.</li>\n  <li>Provide general office administration, including answering phone calls.</li>\n  <li>Highly organized, detail-oriented, and able to thrive in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Support HR and payroll activities as needed.</li>\n  <li>Take on additional administrative or accounts-related tasks when assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
